data.description: Discover the perfect blend of modern updates and classic charm in this 3 bed, 2 bathroom home nestled in a highly sought-after neighborhood. With spacious living areas, quartz kitchen counter tops, and plenty of room to park your RV or boat. Step out onto the covered patio and enjoy your morning coffee or host gatherings in this private outdoor oasis. This home is your ticket to a comfortable and stylish lifestyle.
